  ('ID', 'Boise', 112.0, 65000.0, 4.0, 'standard', 1.0, '{"remote_support": 165.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 225.0, "design_ux": 145.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  Fast-growing tech hub (Micron, HP, Clearwater Analytics). CoL 12% above national and rising rapidly. Low unemployment. Strong SMB density with growing cybersecurity awareness. Buyers are increasingly sophisticated — compete on MDR depth. Market is still less saturated than Seattle/Denver.', 'imported', now()),
  ('IA', 'Davenport', 87.0, 54000.0, 5.5, 'adjusted', 0.8915, '{"remote_support": 145.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 195.0, "design_ux": 125.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  Quad Cities anchor city (IA side). CoL 13% below national. Manufacturing and healthcare dominate. John Deere HQ creates strong industrial/OT cybersecurity awareness. Slightly adjusted rate appropriate; buyers are pragmatic and ROI-focused. Cross-border market with Rock Island/Moline, IL.', 'imported', now()),
  ('IA', 'Hudson', 85.0, 72000.0, 4.5, 'adjusted', 0.8915, '{"remote_support": 145.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 190.0, "design_ux": 125.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  Small Iowa community (Black Hawk County) — not Hudson, WI. CoL ~85, modest income for the area. Manufacturing and agriculture-adjacent professional services are primary prospects. Waterloo/Cedar Falls metro proximity means competition from regional MSPs. Near-adjusted pricing warranted.', 'imported', now()),
  ('LA', 'New Orleans', 96.0, 49000.0, 7.5, 'adjusted', 0.9225, '{"remote_support": 150.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 205.0, "design_ux": 130.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  Unique cultural and economic market. CoL near national average but median income is low. Tourism/hospitality and port/maritime industries have strong PCI and operational continuity needs. Healthcare (Ochsner, LCMC) is the most reliable buyer segment. Post-Katrina resilience culture makes business continuity an easy sell.', 'imported', now()),
  ('MI', 'Grand Rapids', 95.0, 57000.0, 4.5, 'standard', 0.969, '{"remote_support": 150.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 205.0, "design_ux": 130.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  Second-largest MI city and growing. CoL 5% below national, low unemployment. Strong healthcare presence (Spectrum, Corewell) and diverse manufacturing base. Steelcase, Meijer create enterprise-adjacent SMB ecosystem. Buyers are pragmatic Midwesterners — lead with ROI and operational stability.', 'imported', now()),
  ('MI', 'Kalamazoo', 89.0, 48000.0, 5.5, 'adjusted', 0.9225, '{"remote_support": 145.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 195.0, "design_ux": 130.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  Pfizer birthplace and pharma corridor. CoL 11% below national. Life sciences and healthcare buyers have strong HIPAA and data-protection needs — excellent upsell for PLUS tier. Western Michigan University creates education-adjacent IT demand. Slightly adjusted rate appropriate.', 'imported', now()),
  ('MI', 'Lansing', 90.0, 49000.0, 6.5, 'adjusted', 0.9225, '{"remote_support": 145.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 195.0, "design_ux": 130.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  State capital — government and quasi-government anchor the market. CoL 10% below national. GM and auto-adjacent manufacturing supply chain present. Government buyers move slowly but are stable accounts. Compliance framing (CJIS for government, HIPAA for healthcare) is the most effective entry.', 'imported', now()),
  ('MN', 'Minneapolis', 103.0, 63000.0, 4.5, 'standard', 1.0, '{"remote_support": 155.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 215.0, "design_ux": 135.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  Major Midwest financial and healthcare hub (UnitedHealth, Target, Best Buy HQ). CoL near national average. Competitive MSP market with sophisticated buyers. Strong compliance demand (SOX for finance, HIPAA for healthcare). Low unemployment signals healthy SMB market — compete on 24x5 coverage and MDR depth.', 'imported', now()),
  ('MO', 'St. Louis', 88.0, 50000.0, 5.5, 'adjusted', 0.9225, '{"remote_support": 145.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 195.0, "design_ux": 125.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  NOTE: Listed as ''St Louis, IL'' — the major metro is St. Louis, MO (city proper sits in MO; metro spans both states). CoL 12% below national. Strong healthcare (BJC, SSM Health) and financial services base. Washington University and SLU create knowledge-economy adjacency. Adjusted rate appropriate for city-proper; suburban MO markets can support near-standard rates.', 'imported', now()),
  ('OR', 'Portland', 128.0, 75000.0, 5.5, 'premium', 1.155, '{"remote_support": 175.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 245.0, "design_ux": 155.0, "pc_setup": 275.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  NOTE: Listed as ''Portland, WA'' — Portland is in Oregon (OR). CoL 28% above national. Nike, Adidas, Intel, and strong healthcare presence (OHSU, Providence). Growing cybersecurity market — buyers are tech-literate and compare on stack depth. No state income tax in WA pulls some buyers across river to Vancouver, WA.', 'imported', now()),
  ('UT', 'Salt Lake City', 121.0, 58000.0, 3.0, 'standard', 1.0, '{"remote_support": 170.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 235.0, "design_ux": 150.0, "pc_setup": 275.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  Silicon Slopes tech hub (Adobe, Qualtrics, Domo, Goldman Sachs). CoL 21% above national. Very low unemployment. Fast-growing tech ecosystem with strong cybersecurity awareness. Buyers are younger and tech-literate — compete on EDR/MDR depth and cloud security expertise. Healthcare and finance compliance upsell effective.', 'imported', now()),
  ('WI', 'Platteville', 82.0, 44000.0, 5.0, 'secondary', 0.845, '{"remote_support": 140.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 185.0, "design_ux": 125.0, "pc_setup": 225.0}', 'Onboard: Waive/defer  |  Small UW-Platteville college town in rural SW Wisconsin. Very low CoL (~82), modest income. Limited SMB density — agriculture and university are primary anchors. Near-floor pricing required. Long-term play: university IT spin-offs and ag-tech startups may create demand over time.', 'imported', now()),
  ('WI', 'Racine', 88.0, 50000.0, 7.5, 'adjusted', 0.9225, '{"remote_support": 145.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 195.0, "design_ux": 125.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  Lake Michigan manufacturing city (SC Johnson HQ). CoL 12% below national, high unemployment. Manufacturing is the dominant industry — OT/ICS cybersecurity and ransomware protection are primary value drivers. Proximity to Chicago/Milwaukee means buyers compare against metro MSPs. Adjusted rate keeps Ferrum in range.', 'imported', now()),
  ('AZ', 'Tucson', 96.0, 50000.0, 6.0, 'adjusted', 0.9225, '{"remote_support": 150.0, "onsite_block_2hr": 295.0, "onsite_additional": 135.0, "dev_crm": 205.0, "design_ux": 130.0, "pc_setup": 250.0}', 'Onboard: Standard  |  University of Arizona and Davis-Monthan AFB anchor the market. CoL near national average but income is modest. Military/defense clients create CMMC compliance demand. Healthcare (Banner, TMC) is reliable. More price-sensitive than Phoenix — adjusted rate appropriate for competitive positioning.', 'imported', now())
